{
  "_comment": "Single source of truth for all template ids. Append-only — changing order shifts ids. Id 0 reserved as UNSPECIFIED; sequential u16 assigned from 1 in declaration order.",
  "_design_doc": "docs/plans/2026-04-25-template-id-codegen-design.md",

  "_tower_stats_doc": "Tower stats live here as the single source of truth. omoba-template-ids/build.rs reads them and emits TOWER_<NAME>_STATS const + tower_stats(id) lookup, used by base_content tower scripts. 改完 stats 重 build script DLL 即生效，不需動 host 程式碼或 map.json。",
  "_tower_upgrades_doc": "towers[].upgrades = [path0, path1, path2]，每路 4 個 level。每個 entry 有 name/description/cost/effects[]。effects 兩種：{type:stat_mod,key,value,op:add|mul} 或 {type:behavior_flag,flag}。cost 必須符合 upgrade_cost(base, level) = base × {0.25, 0.5, 1.0, 2.5}[level-1]。omoba-template-ids/build.rs 編譯期驗證並 emit TOWER_<NAME>_UPGRADES + tower_upgrades(id) lookup；omb host 端 TowerUpgradeRegistry::new 直接 iterate 此 const。",
